Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.62,0:23:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预告的环节这么快就第11回了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.63,0:24:00.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第11回了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.66,0:24:02.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11是素数吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.24,0:24:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是素数
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.05,0:24:04.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,素数的定义是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.61,0:24:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了1和那个数本身之外没有其它因数的1以外的正整数
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.95,0:24:09.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里素了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.90,0:24:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修饰过多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.26,0:24:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  非素数的定义呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.88,0:24:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是素数的正整数
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.38,0:24:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真素啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.15,0:24:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没化妆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.87,0:24:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预告部分PUZZLE
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.90,0:24:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PUZZLE？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.65,0:24:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PUZZLE和谜题有什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.03,0:24:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,PUZZLE很狡猾  谜题很可恨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.04,0:24:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.61,0:24:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狡猾呢
